Highlights and scores right here.  //on.wvec.com/1FK3E9p   High school football Thursday night special There were several games moved up a day to beat the weather. Here are the highlights. Scott Cash , 13News Now 11:48 p.m. EDT October 1, 2015 CONNECT   
Several games were rescheduled to Thursday night to try and get a jump on the weather. It was still soggy, but there was still plenty of action. We've got highlights from the Lake Taylor vs. Granby and Western Branch vs. Grassfield games.  //on.wvec.com/1FK3E9p TOP VIDEOS
